                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The throng rips and tears at each enemy within its squares and within 5 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:33] save). Damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> Damage [[/r (1d10+12)[slashing],1d6[evil]]]{1d10+12 slashing plus 1d6 evil}</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> Damage [[/r (2d10+12)[slashing],1d6[evil]]]{2d10+12 slashing plus 1d6 evil}</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> Damage [[/r (3d10+12)[slashing],1d6[evil]]]{3d10+12 slashing plus 1d6 evil}</p>"
